name: Excise Duty Report
query:
SELECT si.name AS "Sales Invoice No:Link/Sales Invoice:100", si.customer AS "Customer:Link/Customer:250",
       si.posting_date AS "Invoice Date:Date:100",
       si.base_net_total AS "VAT Exclusive:Currency/currency:200",
       si.base_net_total * 0.09090909  AS "Excise Duty:Currency/currency:200"
FROM `tabSales Invoice` si
WHERE si.excise_duty_applicable
  AND si.posting_date BETWEEN %(from_date)s AND %(to_date)s
